The change comes due to the ongoing KDF recruitment exercise taking place at the same venue something beyond our control as the setup is already in place.

We’ll share the new date and details soon, so stay tuned, my people. 💜
Funny enough, even the Eldoret Culture Connect Fest which was to happen the same day ,was also postponed  looks like October had its own plans 😅

#ManSango #TujiaminiChezaDimba #EkemoniOutNow #GoikaEbeEbuse
